snippet.title: The solution to Johnny Depp's legal battle against the real abuser whose name I need not say
snippet.description:
Yes, it's Amber Heard.

And all I have to say is that it's outrageous and unfair.

Amber Heard is a disgrace of a woman and an insult and middle fingers towards real victims of domestic abuse and survivors of abusive relationships, regardless of their sex.

I will not believe in a woman for whom there is proven and conclusive evidence of her being an abusive and violent person. I am sorry, but this phrase "Believe all women" is a total rubbish and an absolute nonsense with no logic that lacks logic and fundaments.

The solution is simple but tough: do not watch any movie that has this woman in it and do not consume anything produced by any company affiliated with this woman.
